snippet.textDisplay: It's beautiful that you care. Not everyone dares to speak up but it's heartwarming that you care about other people and about the fact that you're never going to finish all that makeup. I think it could supply a lot of makeup artists with ways to use makeup and reduce waste. Especially up and coming makeup artists who have an industry to support. It would be amazing to have a company collect new QUALITY makeup products and fix them to makeup companies or just sell them second hand to people who can pick it up (instead of using more packaging to transport it somewhere else). There's a reason why societies exist.
